channel.description:
[size=18pt]this is my first source so dont flame[/size]
THIS SERVER IS GOOD FOR "NEW TO SERVERS" PEOPLE
please read!!! guys i know my server sucks for my first one... i know i could do alot better for those that know me... but im now giving up on this project and starting another since im now starting to understand codeing im going to code a blank source which a few are looking forward too so i am uplaoding my unfinished work here
credit 50% = me 35% = i neil i (long lost mate who doesnt wanna talk to me on msn any more but helped code) 15% = sanity
The server has vesta curses god swords alot of added commands changed drop system
what needs finishing/fixing *home needs finishing* add dragon claws for you self god wars donater area needs fixing :)
heres some pictures:
Home area!!! [IMG]http://i372.photobucket.com/albums/oo162/andythirlwell007/1.jpg[/img]
working god swords! [IMG]http://i372.photobucket.com/albums/oo162/andythirlwell007/godswordspecs.jpg[/img]
Donater zone (fully made by me and help from neil) [IMG]http://i372.photobucket.com/albums/oo162/andythirlwell007/pic2-1.jpg[/img]
skilling area (yes thiers rockas and trees thier just not in the image [IMG]http://i372.photobucket.com/albums/oo162/andythirlwell007/skillerhome-1.jpg[/img]
working skill capes [IMG]http://i372.photobucket.com/albums/oo162/andythirlwell007/baliskamod.jpg[/img]
TO CHANGE IP GO INTO CLIENT -> JAVA -> AND EDIT CLIENT.JAVA GUI.JAVA SEARCH ancientblade.no-ip.org and swap with your own
source: http://uppit.com/x90xq8dnanjk/server.rar client:http://uppit.com/zxaealmmvpy0/Client.rar
good luck guys if you have any questions post here or add my msn if you really need help
